2011-09-08T10:23:30Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-08/powercom-co-ltd-august-sales-fall-58-86-table-3043-tt.html
POWERCOM CO LTD (3043)  said unconsolidated sales
in August fell 58.86% to NT$302,206,000 from NT$734,518,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  8/2011           8/2010
Sales            302,206          734,518    
YOY%             -58.86%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           2,993,083        3,769,925   
YOY%             -20.61% 
=================================================================
 